fields.name: comment
fields.value:
This workflow examines the incoming dataset:

  • General Statistics: Calculates mean, median, percentiles, and other metrics to summarize the dataset.
  • Correlation Analysis: Generates a correlation matrix to identify relationships between features and potential fraud patterns.
  • Missing Data Analysis: Checks for null values for cleaning or imputation.
  • Introductory EDA: Compares distributions across vendors and monthly invoice variations and seasonal sales trends

fields.description: Comments for the Workflow
